Join us in raising money to support Eden Reforestation Projects’ mission of fostering healthy relationships between communities and the land on which we depend through Landscape Restoration and conservation. Together, we can help restore the environment, mitigate the effects of climate change, and strengthen community resilience for decades to come.  

By working together, we can accomplish so much more and continue to progress closure towards our shared vision of a world where communities thrive in healthy and restored environments.

Thank you for your support.

Thank you for donating to Eden Reforestation Projects through my team's fundraising page for Landscape Restoration and community development.

To make the most significant impact, please share this fundraiser with your family, friends, colleagues, and network to help reach our fundraising goal.  

Thank you for your support.

Dear family and friends,

I am raising money to support Eden Reforestation Projects’ mission of fostering healthy relationships between communities and the land on which we depend through Landscape Restoration and conservation. Together, we can help restore the environment, mitigate the effects of climate change, and strengthen community resilience for decades to come.   

You can directly support global Landscape Restoration and community development by making a donation on my fundraising page today.   

Thank you for your support.

Thank you for donating to Eden Reforestation Projects through my fundraising page for Landscape Restoration and community development.

To make the most significant impact, please share this fundraiser with your family and friends to help reach my fundraising goal.  

Thank you for your support.

Please help me support Eden Reforestation Projects by making a donation through my page. The process is fast, easy and secure. Thanks so much for your support... and please don't forget to send this page to any friends you think might be interested in donating!

Our individual team members have combined digital forces to create this awesome fundraising team. Together we will raise more money for Eden Reforestation Projects than we ever could alone!


Want to help?


Support by making a donation to our team. The process is fast, easy, and secure... and you can be sure that it will benefit a great cause!


Come join the squad!


team-work [teem-wurk] noun


1. A cooperative or coordinated effort on the part of a group of persons acting together as a team or in the interest of a common cause.

We are raising money to support Eden's mission of fostering healthy relationships between communities and the land on which we depend through landscape restoration and conservation. We can help restore the environment, mitigate the effects of climate change, and strengthen community resilience for decades to come.   

By working together, we can accomplish so much more and continue to progress closure towards the shared vision of a world where communities thrive in healthy and restored environments. 

To make the most significant impact, share this page with your family, friends, colleagues, and network to help reach our fundraising goal.   

You can directly support global landscape restoration and community development by donating through this page today.   

Thank you for your support.

Thank you for joining the team! We are combining forces to create this awesome fundraising team.


Together we will raise money for Eden Reforestation Projects to help plant trees and alleviate extreme poverty around the world, and make a greater impact than we could alone!


Want to help?


Support global forest restoration and poverty alleviation by making a donation to our team. The process is fast, easy and secure. Thanks so much for your support. Please don't forget to send this page to any friends you think might be interested in donating!


Please join me in planting trees and saving lives!
